Renowned preacher and General Overseer of the Redeemed Christian Church of God, RCCG, Pastor Enoch Adeboye, on Friday congratulated Vice President, Yemi Osinbajo, on his 62nd birthday. Adeboye, who took to his verified Twitter handle, prayed God to grant Osinbajo strength, wisdom and good health as he marks another year. He made this remark while felicitating with Osinbajo as he celebrates his 62nd birthday. “Happy Birthday Pastor @profosinbajo, I pray that my Daddy will continue to strengthen you and grant you wisdom to surmount all the challenges life brings your way in the name of Jesus,” the tweet read. 